{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/javascript/code-execution/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ejelome"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"16a7fed1-14e8-561d-91f9-542d0924e771","excerpt":"Summary In order to execute JavaScript code, it will need an interpreter.\nInterpreters are provided by host environments, e.g. web browsers and runtime…","html":"<p><strong>Summary</strong></p>\n<p>In order to execute JavaScript code, it will need an interpreter.\nInterpreters are provided by host environments, e.g. web browsers and runtime environments.</p>\n<p>Code can be executed interactively when written directly on the interpreter—\nand on web browsers, through the <em>Browser Console</em>. On larger codebase,\nthey can be written to and executed from either an HTML file or a JavaScript file.</p>\n<p>\n        <div class=\"embedVideo-container\">\n            <iframe\n              title=\"\"\n              width=\"560\"\n              height=\"316\"\n              src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6U_485ypj1A?rel=0\"\n              class=\"embedVideo-iframe\"\n              style=\"border:0\"\n              \n              loading=\"eager\"\n              allowfullscreen\n\t      sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-popups\"\n            ></iframe>\n        </div></p>\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\n<div class=\"toc\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#interpreters\">Interpreters</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#web-browsers\">Web browsers</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#browser-console\">Browser Console</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#html-script-tag\">HTML script tag</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#within-a-script-tag\">Within a script tag</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#from-a-javascript-file\">From a JavaScript file</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#runtime-environments\">Runtime environments</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#from-the-repl\">From the REPL</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#from-a-javascript-file-1\">From a Javascript file</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"interpreters\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#interpreters\" aria-label=\"interpreters permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Interpreters</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>To execute JavaScript code, it requires an interpreter</li>\n<li>Interpreters are provided by web browsers and runtime environments</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"web-browsers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#web-browsers\" aria-label=\"web browsers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Web browsers</h3>\n<p>Web browsers, e.g. Safari, provide client-side interpreters.</p>\n<p>There are two ways to execute JavaScript code in web browsers:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Through the <em>Browser Console</em></li>\n<li>or through the HTML script tag</li>\n</ol>\n<p>As an example, let’s use Safari, the default web browser for macOS.</p>\n<h4 id=\"browser-console\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#browser-console\" aria-label=\"browser console permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Browser Console</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The Browser Console executes written code interactively, i.e. the feedback is instant after submission.\nIt is used primarily for debugging but is also commonly used to execute snippets of code.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Open Safari</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d3876eaead5001e90f1fe40982250f0e/6149e/safari-with-google-as-homepage.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.49367088607595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Safari with google as homepage\"\n        title=\"Safari with google as homepage\"\n        src=\"/static/d3876eaead5001e90f1fe40982250f0e/f058b/safari-with-google-as-homepage.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d3876eaead5001e90f1fe40982250f0e/c26ae/safari-with-google-as-homepage.png 158w,\n/static/d3876eaead5001e90f1fe40982250f0e/6bdcf/safari-with-google-as-homepage.png 315w,\n/static/d3876eaead5001e90f1fe40982250f0e/f058b/safari-with-google-as-homepage.png 630w,\n/static/d3876eaead5001e90f1fe40982250f0e/40601/safari-with-google-as-homepage.png 945w,\n/static/d3876eaead5001e90f1fe40982250f0e/78612/safari-with-google-as-homepage.png 1260w,\n/static/d3876eaead5001e90f1fe40982250f0e/6149e/safari-with-google-as-homepage.png 2784w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>First, enable <em>Develop menu</em></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <code class=\"language-text\">Safari</code> > <code class=\"language-text\">Preferences...</code> > <code class=\"language-text\">Advanced</code></li>\n<li>\n<p>then tick <code class=\"language-text\">Show Develop menu in menu bar</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1148ac8472018ffcb7065aea24861a86/f98ee/show-develop-menu-in-menu-bar.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.22784810126582%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Show Develop menu in menu bar\"\n        title=\"Show Develop menu in menu bar\"\n        src=\"/static/1148ac8472018ffcb7065aea24861a86/f058b/show-develop-menu-in-menu-bar.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1148ac8472018ffcb7065aea24861a86/c26ae/show-develop-menu-in-menu-bar.png 158w,\n/static/1148ac8472018ffcb7065aea24861a86/6bdcf/show-develop-menu-in-menu-bar.png 315w,\n/static/1148ac8472018ffcb7065aea24861a86/f058b/show-develop-menu-in-menu-bar.png 630w,\n/static/1148ac8472018ffcb7065aea24861a86/40601/show-develop-menu-in-menu-bar.png 945w,\n/static/1148ac8472018ffcb7065aea24861a86/78612/show-develop-menu-in-menu-bar.png 1260w,\n/static/1148ac8472018ffcb7065aea24861a86/f98ee/show-develop-menu-in-menu-bar.png 1808w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Open Console tab</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Right click then select <code class=\"language-text\">Inspect Element</code> or press <code class=\"language-text\">command+option+i</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 376px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bd7293a32c7c2b38dac00899d775ec8b/d38a6/right-click-to-display-context-menu.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Right click to display context menu\"\n        title=\"Right click to display context menu\"\n        src=\"/static/bd7293a32c7c2b38dac00899d775ec8b/d38a6/right-click-to-display-context-menu.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bd7293a32c7c2b38dac00899d775ec8b/c26ae/right-click-to-display-context-menu.png 158w,\n/static/bd7293a32c7c2b38dac00899d775ec8b/6bdcf/right-click-to-display-context-menu.png 315w,\n/static/bd7293a32c7c2b38dac00899d775ec8b/d38a6/right-click-to-display-context-menu.png 376w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 376px) 100vw, 376px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Select <code class=\"language-text\">Console</code> tab or press <code class=\"language-text\">command+option+c</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/81cfcf525364491c99655e6e50a7bece/6149e/console-tab.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.49367088607595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Console tab\"\n        title=\"Console tab\"\n        src=\"/static/81cfcf525364491c99655e6e50a7bece/f058b/console-tab.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/81cfcf525364491c99655e6e50a7bece/c26ae/console-tab.png 158w,\n/static/81cfcf525364491c99655e6e50a7bece/6bdcf/console-tab.png 315w,\n/static/81cfcf525364491c99655e6e50a7bece/f058b/console-tab.png 630w,\n/static/81cfcf525364491c99655e6e50a7bece/40601/console-tab.png 945w,\n/static/81cfcf525364491c99655e6e50a7bece/78612/console-tab.png 1260w,\n/static/81cfcf525364491c99655e6e50a7bece/6149e/console-tab.png 2784w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Write the code then press <code class=\"language-text\">enter</code> to submit</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3c1cfce5eefd7f783259796a9a872de4/6149e/evaluate-javascript-code.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.49367088607595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Evaluate JavaScript code\"\n        title=\"Evaluate JavaScript code\"\n        src=\"/static/3c1cfce5eefd7f783259796a9a872de4/f058b/evaluate-javascript-code.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3c1cfce5eefd7f783259796a9a872de4/c26ae/evaluate-javascript-code.png 158w,\n/static/3c1cfce5eefd7f783259796a9a872de4/6bdcf/evaluate-javascript-code.png 315w,\n/static/3c1cfce5eefd7f783259796a9a872de4/f058b/evaluate-javascript-code.png 630w,\n/static/3c1cfce5eefd7f783259796a9a872de4/40601/evaluate-javascript-code.png 945w,\n/static/3c1cfce5eefd7f783259796a9a872de4/78612/evaluate-javascript-code.png 1260w,\n/static/3c1cfce5eefd7f783259796a9a872de4/6149e/evaluate-javascript-code.png 2784w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"html-script-tag\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#html-script-tag\" aria-label=\"html script tag permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTML script tag</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Code written in a file requires reloading the web browser after each save in order to see the changes.\nThis is how JavaScript programs are normally written to maintain a larger codebase.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h5 id=\"within-a-script-tag\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#within-a-script-tag\" aria-label=\"within a script tag permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Within a script tag</h5>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create an HTML file (e.g. <code class=\"language-text\">index.html</code>)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token function\">touch</span> index.html</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Write the code inside <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script&gt;</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"hello, world\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Then save the file.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>NOTES</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>The <code class=\"language-text\">console</code> object provides access to Browser Console</li>\n<li>The <code class=\"language-text\">.log</code> method outputs a standard text to the console</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Open the HTML file in a web browser</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token function\">open</span> index.html</code></pre></div>\n<p>Then see the result output on the <em>Browser Console</em>.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h5 id=\"from-a-javascript-file\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#from-a-javascript-file\" aria-label=\"from a javascript file permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>From a JavaScript file</h5>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create a JavaScript file (e.g. <code class=\"language-text\">scripts.js</code>)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token function\">touch</span> scripts.js</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Write the code in the JavaScript file</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"hello, world\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Then save the file.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create an HTML file (e.g. <code class=\"language-text\">index.html</code>)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ touch index.html</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Link the JavaScript file</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>./scripts.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Open the HTML file in a web browser</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token function\">open</span> index.html</code></pre></div>\n<p>Then see the result output on the <em>Browser Console</em>.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"runtime-environments\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#runtime-environments\" aria-label=\"runtime environments permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Runtime environments</h3>\n<p>Runtime environments, e.g. Node.js, provide server-side interpreters.</p>\n<p>There are also two ways to execute JavaScript code in runtime environments:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Through the REPL</li>\n<li>Through a JavaScript file</li>\n</ol>\n<p>As an example, let’s use Node.js, one of the host environments for JavaScript.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Install Node.js via its official <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download\">installer</a> or through <a href=\"https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm\">nvm</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"from-the-repl\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#from-the-repl\" aria-label=\"from the repl permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>From the REPL</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The REPL is an interactive shell that can execute JavaScript code similar to Browser Console but without needing web browsers.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Open <code class=\"language-text\">node</code> interpreter</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ node\nWelcome to Node.js v15.13.0.\nType <span class=\"token string\">\".help\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token function\">more</span> information.\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Write the code then press <code class=\"language-text\">enter</code> to submit</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">Welcome to Node.js v15.13.0.\nType <span class=\"token string\">\".help\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token function\">more</span> information.\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"hello, world\"</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'hello, world'</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n<span class=\"token boolean\">true</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"from-a-javascript-file-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#from-a-javascript-file-1\" aria-label=\"from a javascript file 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>From a Javascript file</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Code written in a file requires that the file be re-executed after each save in order to see the changes.\nIn similar fashion like in web browsers, this is how JavaScript programs are also written to maintain a larger codebase except that it is on the server-side.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create a JavaScript file (e.g. <code class=\"language-text\">app.js</code>)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token function\">touch</span> app.js</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Write the code in the JavaScript file</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"hello, world\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Then save the file.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Execute the file</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ node app.js\nhello, world\n<span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token boolean\">true</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"JavaScript: Code Execution","date":"April 07, 2021","description":"A short tour on how to execute JavaScript code."}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript/history/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"JavaScript: History"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript/crash-course/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"JavaScript: Crash Course"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"16a7fed1-14e8-561d-91f9-542d0924e771","previousPostId":"5e3ec4d5-5a33-5f9f-a86a-f856784a4ec3","nextPostId":"6af3aa91-cb61-5638-89fa-94e618c27ca2"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3336637013"]}